_sText:
I was bored and I decided to make one deathrun map.

IT is not large but if you want same map with more traps just leave that in comment, or if you spot bug.
When CT finish a map he can chose four ways to end a round: 
- AWP
- Bhop
- Gun
- Knife Fight

JUST WHEN TESTING A MAP ( WHEN THERE IS NO TERRORIST IN GAME BUTTONS ARE ALL KIND OF COLORS !!! )

And name of map is my real name Slavko.
